        protected boolean isSuffix(java.lang.String suffix)
        Checks to see if the given suffix leads to a word down this branch. This is a recursive function.
        Parameters:
        suffix - The String representing the suffix.
        Returns:
        Whether or not the given suffix leads to a word. Returns false if the suffix does not lead to a word.

      • getNode

        Parameters:

        Returns:
